News Corp. Director Perkins Says He’s Leaving Company at 79 Because of Age

-- B y   C a r o l   H y m o w i t z
-- 
2011-09-02T15:31:16Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-02/news-corp-director-perkins-says-he-s-leaving-company-at-79-because-of-age.html
News Corp. (NWSA)  director  Tom Perkins  said
he’s resigning from the board because of his age.  Perkins, 79, said in an interview today that he started to
discuss his stepping down several months ago.  To contact the reporter on this story:
